data.description: Come join us for one floor living nestled along the Saybrook coastline. Begin your experience as you enter this home’s spacious foyer appointed with octagonal tray ceiling and gracious chandelier that completes the look of elegance in every way. A pleasant atmosphere that will support the grandest of gatherings while at the same time offering areas throughout for intimate conversation. Large kitchen with granite countertops, views overlooking the inground pool, dining area,Great room and large three season screened room with Cathedral pine ceilings. Bedrooms are balanced away from the living area for privacy. Master suite flows into the master bath with hydro tub perfect for relaxing after a long day. Walk in closet completes the master suite. Located on a private road with easy access to I-95, Route 9, Amtrak train stations, beaches, shopping, golf, The Kate, and so much more to see within driving distance. Halfway between Boston and New York by train.
